library(tidyverse)
library(furrr)

get_bayes <- function(x) {
  -(length(x) + 1) / (sum(log(x)) -1)
}

get_mle <- function(x) {
  -length(x) / sum(log(x))
}

draw_sims <- function(n) {
  rbeta(n, shape1 = 2, shape2 = 1)
}


run_sim <- function(n, get_est, base_seed = 1693) {
  future_map_dbl(1:50000, \(i) draw_sims(n) |> get_est(),
                 .options = furrr_options(seed = base_seed))
}

get_bias_variance <- function(n, get_est) {
  sims <- run_sim(n, get_est)
  tibble(n = n,
         bias = mean(sims) - 2,
         variance = var(sims))
}

plan(multisession, workers = 16)

n_seq <- c(1:10 * 10, 2:5 * 100)

mle_results <- map_dfr(n_seq, \(n) get_bias_variance(n, get_mle))

bayes_results <- map_dfr(n_seq, \(n) get_bias_variance(n, get_bayes))

mle_results |> 
  mutate(rmse = sqrt(bias^2 + variance),
         bscale1 = abs(bias) * sqrt(n),
         vscale1 = variance * sqrt(n),
         bscale2 = abs(bias) * n, 
         vscale2 = variance * n)

mle_results |> 
  mutate(bias_scaled1 = abs(bias) * sqrt(n),
         bias_scaled2 = abs(bias) * n) |> 
  pivot_longer(cols = starts_with("bias_scaled"),
               names_to = "scaling",
               values_to = "scaled_bias") |> 
  ggplot(aes(n, scaled_bias, color = scaling)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  labs(title = "MLE Bias Scaled by sqrt(n), n",
       x = "Sample Size (n)",
       y = "Scaled Bias") +
  theme_minimal()
